text: Samsul Muhidin Pellu (born 21 September 1995) is an Indonesian professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for Liga 2 club Martapura.Samsul Pellu ==Career== ===Bali United=== He made his debut in the Liga 1 on April 16, 2017 against Madura United.Madura United 2-0 Bali United ==References== ==External links== * * * Samsul Pellu at Official website TSC Category:Indonesian footballers Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:People from Tulehu Category:Sportspeople from Maluku (province) Category:Bali United F.C. players Category:Liga 1 (Indonesia) players
